## Navigation Patterns

### Mobile Hamburger Menu (Alpine.js)
```html
<nav x-data="{ open: false }">
    <div class="flex items-center justify-between">
        <!-- Desktop links (always visible on md+) -->
        <div class="hidden md:flex md:items-center md:space-x-4">
            <a href="/">Home</a>
        </div>

        <!-- Mobile menu button (hidden on md+) -->
        <button @click="open = !open" class="md:hidden p-2 rounded-md"
                aria-label="Toggle menu" :aria-expanded="open">
            <svg x-show="!open" class="h-6 w-6"><!-- Hamburger icon --></svg>
            <svg x-show="open" x-cloak class="h-6 w-6"><!-- Close icon --></svg>
        </button>
    </div>

    <!-- Mobile dropdown menu -->
    <div x-show="open" x-cloak @click.away="open = false" class="md:hidden pb-3">
        <a href="/" class="block px-3 py-2">Home</a>
    </div>
</nav>
```

**Key Patterns:**
- Use Alpine.js `x-data`, `x-show`, `@click` for interactivity
- `x-cloak` prevents flash of unstyled content (requires CSS: `[x-cloak] { display: none !important; }`)
- `@click.away` closes menu when clicking outside
- Separate desktop (`hidden md:flex`) and mobile (`md:hidden`) nav sections
- Always include ARIA labels: `aria-label="Toggle menu"`, `:aria-expanded="open"`

## Header Patterns

### Base Header Structure
```html
<header class="bg-white shadow md:sticky md:top-0 z-50">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
        <div class="flex justify-between items-center h-16">
            <!-- Logo -->
            <a href="/" class="flex items-center">
                <img src="{% static 'images/vixxo-logo.svg' %}" alt="Vixxo" class="h-8">
            </a>
            <!-- Actions (Sign In button, user menu) -->
        </div>
    </div>
</header>
```

**Key Classes:**
- `md:sticky md:top-0` - Sticky header on desktop only (preserves mobile vertical space)
- `h-16` - Fixed header height (64px)
- `z-50` - High z-index to stay above content

### Sign In Button
```html
<a href="{% url 'entra_login' %}"
   class="bg-vixxo-primary text-white px-4 py-2 rounded-md hover:bg-vixxo-secondary transition-colors focus:ring-2 focus:ring-vixxo-primary focus:ring-offset-2">
    Sign In
</a>
```

**Note:** Always use Django's `{% url %}` template tag instead of hardcoded URLs.

**Key Classes:**
- `bg-vixxo-primary` - Primary brand color
- `hover:bg-vixxo-secondary` - Hover state
- `focus:ring-2 focus:ring-vixxo-primary` - Accessible focus state

## Footer Patterns

### Base Footer Structure
```html
<footer class="bg-white border-t border-gray-200 mt-auto">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 py-6">
        <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row justify-between items-center space-y-4 md:space-y-0">
            <div class="text-sm text-vixxo-dark">
                &copy; {% now "Y" %} Vixxo. All rights reserved.
            </div>
            <nav class="flex flex-wrap justify-center md:justify-end space-x-4">
                <!-- Footer links -->
            </nav>
        </div>
    </div>
</footer>
```

**Key Classes:**
- `mt-auto` - Pushes footer to bottom (used with flex layout)
- `flex-col md:flex-row` - Stacked on mobile, horizontal on desktop
- `space-x-4` - Horizontal spacing between links
